>Jzil GSix が現われ、Drakis Bloodcaster が消えました。
>
>You say, 'Hail Jzil GSix'
>Jzil GSix says 'Ah, so you have come to be tested.  Many fine things 
>can be your reward.  There are three tests I can administer. Will you 
>take the test of flight, power, or mind?  I also am in search of a item 
>you might have gotten from me and are willing to trade back. 
>
>You say, 'I choose flight.'
>Jzil GSix says 'So, you wish to start upon the test of flight? So be 
>it.  You must return to me a verdant tessera, an ebon shard, and a 
>griffon's beak to reap your rewards.  May the darkness guide your 
>steps. 
>
>You say, 'I choose power.'
>Jzil GSix says 'The test of power it is.  Prove yourself worthy of 
>power and bring me a silver disk, spiroc feathers, and a black silk 
>cape.  Only then will you know true power. 
>
>You say, 'I choose mind.'
>Jzil GSix says 'The test of mind it shall be.  You must return to me, 
>from this place of air and mist, a rugous globe, some djinni blood, and 
>fine cloth raiment.  Then, and only then, you shall have the reward you 
>deserve! 
>
>You say, 'What trade back?'
>Jzil GSix says 'I am searching for a Rotted Griffon-Hide Wrist Guard so 
>I can replace them with the Wrist Guard Ive just mastered creating. 
